  "description": "A long, expansive shot of the Golden Gate Bridge stretching across a body of water, likely the San Francisco Bay. The bridge is a vibrant orange-red color and appears relatively small in the frame due to the distance. The water is a deep blue, with subtle wave patterns creating a textured surface. Above the bridge is a dramatic sky filled with billowing, grey and white clouds. The clouds are densely packed and create a sense of depth and movement. The distant hills and landmasses are faintly visible through the haze, adding to the overall atmospheric perspective. The lighting is soft and diffused, contributing to a calming effect.",
